**  ERR-MSG
E-01 OPTION SHOULD BE 0, 1 OR 2
E-02 CODE IS INVALID
E-03 CODE IS NOT IN MASTER FILE
E-04 CODE IS ALREADY CANCELLED
E-05 CODE IS NOT IN MASTER FILE
